claim.claim-text:
1. A tissue particle harvester assembly comprising:
a housing including an internal flushing container;
a port in the housing;
a cap configured to fit over the internal flushing container;
a rotatable shaft extending through a cylindrical body;
a tissue cutting tool mounted on the rotatable shaft, wherein the tissue cutting tool is received within an open cutting face of the housing, and the cap is further configured to restrict fluid movement across the open cutting face of the housing;
an electric motor coupled to the rotatable shaft; and
a mechanical agitator.

7. A tissue particle harvester assembly comprising:
a housing;
a tissue cutting tool received within the housing;
a mechanical agitator; and
an electric motor coupled to the tissue cutting tool, where:
the tissue cutting tool comprises:

a cylindrical body including a first end, a second end, and a cutting surface between the first and second end;
a shaft extending through a center of the first end and the second end;
a slot formed in the first end and extending into the cutting surface;
a cutting feature inserted into the slot; and
an internal core having at least one channel for fluid flow and configured to remain stationary with respect to the housing when the cutting surface is rotated with respect to the housing.
